# Title: ImagingDevices Unusual Parent/Child Processes
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-09-27
# Level: high
# Description: Detects unusual parent or children of the ImagingDevices.exe (Windows Contacts) process as seen being used with Bumblebee activity
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.execution
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_imagingdevices_unusual_parents.yml

ParentImage="*\\ImagingDevices.exe" OR (Image="*\\ImagingDevices.exe" ParentImage IN ("*\\WmiPrvSE.exe", "*\\svchost.exe", "*\\dllhost.exe"))